       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *           I D E N T I F I C A T I O N   D I V I S I O N        *
      ******************************************************************
       PROGRAM-ID. COB06100.
      ******************************************************************
      *                                                                *
      *     Reconciliacao de Movimentos Bancarios a Credito            *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
      * Descri誽o da funcionalidade                                    *
      * - Obtem de forma automatica a Invoice correspondente aos       *
      *   movimentos bancarios extraidos pelo robo                     *
      ******************************************************************
      *           L O G     D E     A L T E R A C O E S                *
      ******************************************************************
      *  INICIO  * AUTOR  * FIM    *  C O M E N T A R I O S            *
      *          *        *        *                                   *
      *          *        *        *                                   *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *           E N V I R O N M E N T         D I V I S I O N        *
      ******************************************************************
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                     CONFIGURATION SECTION                      *
      ******************************************************************
       SOURCE-COMPUTER. IBM-AS400.
       OBJECT-COMPUTER. IBM-AS400.
       SPECIAL-NAMES.
           DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
      ******************************************************************
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                      INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION                      *
      ******************************************************************
       FILE-CONTROL.
      ******************************************************************
       DATA DIVISION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                   D A T A   D I V I S I O N                    *
      ******************************************************************
       FILE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                          FILE SECTION                          *
      ******************************************************************
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                    WORKING STORAGE SECTION                     *
      ******************************************************************
      *
      ******************************************************************
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      ******************************************************************
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5013 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD6405 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD6900 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.

      ******************************************************************
      * CONSTANTES
      ******************************************************************
       01  CONSTANTES.
           05 WS-PROGNAME              PIC  X(10) VALUE 'COB06100'.
           05 CON-COVT5013             PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COVT5013'.
           05 CON-COVT6405             PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COVT6405'.
           05 CON-COVT6900             PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COVT6900'.
           05 CON-CS-2                 PIC  X(01) VALUE '2'.
           05 CON-S                    PIC  X(01) VALUE 'S'.
           05 CON-CR                   PIC  X(02) VALUE 'CR'.
           05 CON-DATE-MIN             PIC  X(10) VALUE '0001-01-01'.

      ******************************************************************
      * VARIAVEIS
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-DATA-SEARCH            PIC  X(10)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-DATA-MINIMA            PIC  X(10)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-DATA-HOJE              PIC  X(10)  VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-NSEQ                   PIC S9(10)  COMP-3 VALUE ZEROES.

      ******************************************************************
      *  SWITCH
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-SWITCHES.
           05 WS-STATUS-COT69       PIC S9(03) VALUE 0.
              88 WS-COT69-OK                   VALUE 0.
              88 WS-COT69-NOTFND               VALUE 100.

      ******************************************************************
      * COPYS
      ******************************************************************
           COPY AQCL0001.
           COPY AQCW0109.
           COPY VIAL0015.
           COPY VIAW0011.
           COPY VIAW0012.
           COPY VIATK001.
           COPY VIATK002.
           COPY COCK0002.
           COPY COCF3100.
           COPY VIAL1000.

      ******************************************************************
      * DB2
      ******************************************************************
       01  WS-CURSOR-VARS.
           05 FILLER                     PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.

      *
      * MOVIMENTOS BANCARIOS A CREDITO
      *
           EXEC SQL
                DECLARE COT69 CURSOR FOR
                SELECT
                       CPAIS
                     , CBANCO
                     , CCONTA
                     , DDATMOV
                     , NSEQMOV
                     , DDATVAL
                     , CTIPOMOV
                     , NVALMOV
                     , CMOEDA
                     , GDESMOV
                     , NSALDCNT
                     , CEMPRESA
                     , IRECON
                     , GREFINV
                     , NINVREC
                 FROM COVT6900_MOVBANC
                 WHERE  IRECON  <> :CON-S
                   AND  CTIPOMOV = :CON-CR
              ORDER BY CPAIS
                     , CBANCO
                     , CCONTA
                     , DDATMOV
                     , NSEQMOV
              FOR UPDATE OF
                       IRECON
                     , GREFINV
                     , NINVREC
           END-EXEC.

      ******************************************************************
       01  FILLER              PIC X(40) VALUE 'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE'.
      ******************************************************************
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      ******************************************************************
      *                        LINKAGE SECTION                         *
      ******************************************************************
           COPY AQCW0009.
      ******************************************************************
       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING AQCW0009-DATA.
      ******************************************************************
      *              P R O C E D U R E   D I V I S I O N               *
      ******************************************************************
       0000-MAINLINE.
      ******************************************************************
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
                 THRU 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 3000-FIM-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3000-FIM-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0000-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           GOBACK.

      ******************************************************************
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA'      TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM AQCP0100-REG-INICIO
                 THRU AQCP0100-REG-INICIO-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM AQCP0100-OBT-DADOS-ARQ
                 THRU AQCP0100-OBT-DADOS-ARQ-EXIT
           END-IF.

       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA'        TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-OPEN-CURSOR
                 THRU 2200-OPEN-CURSOR-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2300-FETCH-CURSOR
                 THRU 2300-FETCH-CURSOR-EXIT

              PERFORM 2400-PROC-CURSOR
                 THRU 2400-PROC-CURSOR-EXIT
                      UNTIL NOT DB2-OK
                         OR NOT AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS

              EXEC SQL
                   CLOSE COT69
              END-EXEC
           END-IF.

       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2200-OPEN-CURSOR.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2200-OPEN-CURSOR'          TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE DCLCOCD6900.

           EXEC SQL
                OPEN COT69
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT6900        TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2200-OPEN-CURSOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2300-FETCH-CURSOR.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2300-FETCH-CURSOR'         TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
              FETCH  COT69
               INTO
                    :COCD6900-CPAIS
                  , :COCD6900-CBANCO
                  , :COCD6900-CCONTA
                  , :COCD6900-DDATMOV
                  , :COCD6900-NSEQMOV
                  , :COCD6900-DDATVAL
                  , :COCD6900-CTIPOMOV
                  , :COCD6900-NVALMOV
                  , :COCD6900-CMOEDA
                  , :COCD6900-GDESMOV
                  , :COCD6900-NSALDCNT
                  , :COCD6900-CEMPRESA
                  , :COCD6900-IRECON
                  , :COCD6900-GREFINV
                  , :COCD6900-NINVREC
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT6900        TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
           WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2300-FETCH-CURSOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2400-PROC-CURSOR.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2400-PROC-CURSOR'          TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2500-TRATA-INVOICE
                 THRU 2500-TRATA-INVOICE-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2300-FETCH-CURSOR
                 THRU 2300-FETCH-CURSOR-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2400-PROC-CURSOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2500-TRATA-INVOICE.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2500-TRATA-INVOICE'       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE                       DCLCOCD5013

           MOVE COCD6900-CMOEDA        TO COCD5013-CMOEDA.
           MOVE COCD6900-CEMPRESA      TO COCD5013-CEMPRESA.

           EXEC SQL
                SELECT  NIDINVOICE
                     ,  NIDPROJECTO
                     ,  GCLIENTE
                     ,  DDATAINSER
                     ,  DDATAEMISS
                     ,  DDATAEMIS2
                     ,  DDATEDUE
                     ,  CPRAZO
                     ,  NTOTALAMOUNT
                     ,  NTAXAMOUNT
                     ,  GDESCINVOICE
                     ,  CSTATUS
                     ,  CUSERID
                     ,  HTIMEST
                     ,  GREFINV
                     ,  DPAG
                     ,  CTIPDOC
                     ,  CMOEDA
                     ,  CIMPOSTO
                     ,  NOTAS
                     ,  NTOTCTRV
                     ,  NTAXCTRV
                     ,  CTIPFAC
                     ,  NTOTPAG
                     ,  NTAXPAG
                     ,  NTOTRET
                     ,  NTAXRET
                     ,  GREFNCR
                     ,  DDATEMINCR
                     ,  CMOTANU
                     ,  CTIPANU
                     ,  CEMPRESA
                     ,  IRECON
                     ,  DDATMOV
                     ,  NSEQMOV
                     ,  NTOTNCR
                     ,  NTAXNCR
                     ,  CPAIS
                     ,  CBANCO
                     ,  CCONTA
                  INTO :COCD5013-NIDINVOICE
                     , :COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO
                     , :COCD5013-GCLIENTE
                     , :COCD5013-DDATAINSER
                     , :COCD5013-DDATAEMISS
                     , :COCD5013-DDATAEMIS2
                     , :COCD5013-DDATEDUE
                     , :COCD5013-CPRAZO
                     , :COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , :COCD5013-NTAXAMOUNT
                     , :COCD5013-GDESCINVOICE
                     , :COCD5013-CSTATUS
                     , :COCD5013-CUSERID
                     , :COCD5013-HTIMEST
                     , :COCD5013-GREFINV
                     , :COCD5013-DPAG
                     , :COCD5013-CTIPDOC
                     , :COCD5013-CMOEDA
                     , :COCD5013-CIMPOSTO
                     , :COCD5013-NOTAS
                     , :COCD5013-NTOTCTRV
                     , :COCD5013-NTAXCTRV
                     , :COCD5013-CTIPFAC
                     , :COCD5013-NTOTPAG
                     , :COCD5013-NTAXPAG
                     , :COCD5013-NTOTRET
                     , :COCD5013-NTAXRET
                     , :COCD5013-GREFNCR
                     , :COCD5013-DDATEMINCR
                     , :COCD5013-CMOTANU
                     , :COCD5013-CTIPANU
                     , :COCD5013-CEMPRESA
                     , :COCD5013-IRECON
                     , :COCD5013-DDATMOV
                     , :COCD5013-NSEQMOV
                     , :COCD5013-NTOTNCR
                     , :COCD5013-NTAXNCR
                     , :COCD5013-CPAIS
                     , :COCD5013-CBANCO
                     , :COCD5013-CCONTA
                  FROM  COVT5013_INVOICES
                 WHERE  CSTATUS     =  :CON-CS-2
                   AND  CMOEDA      =  :COCD5013-CMOEDA
                   AND  CEMPRESA    =  :COCD5013-CEMPRESA
                   AND  IRECON      <> :CON-S
                   AND  NTOTALAMOUNT +
                        NTAXAMOUNT   -
                        NTOTPAG      -
                        NTAXPAG      -
                        NTOTRET      -
                        NTAXRET      = :COCD6900-NVALMOV
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT5013           TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
                PERFORM 2510-TRATA-PAG
                   THRU 2510-TRATA-PAG-EXIT

           WHEN DB2-NOTFND
           WHEN DB2-DUPLINE
                CONTINUE

           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2500-TRATA-INVOICE-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2510-TRATA-PAG.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2510-TRATA-PAG'           TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2600-INS-INVPAY
              THRU 2600-INS-INVPAY-EXIT

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2700-UPD-INVOICES
                 THRU 2700-UPD-INVOICES-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2800-UPD-MOV-BANC
                 THRU 2800-UPD-MOV-BANC-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2510-TRATA-PAG-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2600-INS-INVPAY.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2600-INS-INVPAY'        TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCD5013-NIDINVOICE      TO COCD6405-NIDINVOICE
           MOVE COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO     TO COCD6405-NIDPROJECTO
           MOVE COCD5013-GCLIENTE        TO COCD6405-GCLIENTE
           MOVE COCD5013-DDATAINSER      TO COCD6405-DDATAINSER
           MOVE COCD5013-DDATAEMISS      TO COCD6405-DDATAEMISS
           MOVE COCD5013-DDATAEMIS2      TO COCD6405-DDATAEMIS2
           MOVE COCD5013-DDATEDUE        TO COCD6405-DDATEDUE
           MOVE COCD5013-CPRAZO          TO COCD6405-CPRAZO
           MOVE COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT    TO COCD6405-NTOTALAMOUNT
           MOVE COCD5013-NTAXAMOUNT      TO COCD6405-NTAXAMOUNT
           MOVE COCD5013-GDESCINVOICE    TO COCD6405-GDESCINVOICE
           MOVE COCK0002-CSTATUS-PAG     TO COCD6405-CSTATUS
           MOVE WS-PROGNAME              TO COCD6405-CUSERID
           MOVE COCD5013-GREFINV         TO COCD6405-GREFINV
           MOVE COCD6900-DDATMOV         TO COCD6405-DPAG
           MOVE COCD5013-CTIPDOC         TO COCD6405-CTIPDOC
           MOVE COCD5013-CMOEDA          TO COCD6405-CMOEDA
           MOVE COCD5013-CIMPOSTO        TO COCD6405-CIMPOSTO
           MOVE COCD5013-NOTAS           TO COCD6405-NOTAS
           MOVE COCD5013-NTOTCTRV        TO COCD6405-NTOTCTRV
           MOVE COCD5013-NTAXCTRV        TO COCD6405-NTAXCTRV
           MOVE COCD5013-CTIPFAC         TO COCD6405-CTIPFAC

           COMPUTE COCD6405-NTOTPAG =  COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT -
                                      (COCD5013-NTOTPAG +
                                       COCD5013-NTOTRET)

           COMPUTE COCD6405-NTAXPAG =  COCD5013-NTAXAMOUNT -
                                      (COCD5013-NTAXPAG +
                                       COCD5013-NTAXRET)

           MOVE COCD5013-NTOTRET         TO COCD6405-NTOTRET
           MOVE COCD5013-NTAXRET         TO COCD6405-NTAXRET
           MOVE SPACES                   TO COCD6405-CTIPMOV
           MOVE CON-S                    TO COCD6405-IRECON
           MOVE COCD6900-DDATMOV         TO COCD6405-DDATMOV
           MOVE COCD6900-NSEQMOV         TO COCD6405-NSEQMOV
           MOVE SPACES                   TO COCD6405-GREFNCR
           MOVE CON-DATE-MIN             TO COCD6405-DDATEMINCR
           MOVE COCD6900-CPAIS           TO COCD6405-CPAIS
           MOVE COCD6900-CBANCO          TO COCD6405-CBANCO
           MOVE COCD6900-CCONTA          TO COCD6405-CCONTA

           PERFORM 2610-OBTEM-SEQ
              THRU 2610-OBTEM-SEQ-EXIT

           IF AQCW0009-SEM-ERROS

              EXEC SQL
                   INSERT INTO COVT6405_INVPAY
                   (
                      NIDINVOICE
                    , NSEQ
                    , NIDPROJECTO
                    , GCLIENTE
                    , DDATAINSER
                    , DDATAEMISS
                    , DDATAEMIS2
                    , DDATEDUE
                    , CPRAZO
                    , NTOTALAMOUNT
                    , NTAXAMOUNT
                    , GDESCINVOICE
                    , CSTATUS
                    , CUSERID
                    , HTIMEST
                    , GREFINV
                    , DPAG
                    , CTIPDOC
                    , CMOEDA
                    , CIMPOSTO
                    , NOTAS
                    , NTOTCTRV
                    , NTAXCTRV
                    , CTIPFAC
                    , NTOTPAG
                    , NTAXPAG
                    , NTOTRET
                    , NTAXRET
                    , CTIPMOV
                    , IRECON
                    , DDATMOV
                    , NSEQMOV
                    , GREFNCR
                    , DDATEMINCR
                    , CPAIS
                    , CBANCO
                    , CCONTA
                   )
                   VALUES (
                          :COCD6405-NIDINVOICE
                        , :COCD6405-NSEQ
                        , :COCD6405-NIDPROJECTO
                        , :COCD6405-GCLIENTE
                        , :COCD6405-DDATAINSER
                        , :COCD6405-DDATAEMISS
                        , :COCD6405-DDATAEMIS2
                        , :COCD6405-DDATEDUE
                        , :COCD6405-CPRAZO
                        , :COCD6405-NTOTALAMOUNT
                        , :COCD6405-NTAXAMOUNT
                        , :COCD6405-GDESCINVOICE
                        , :COCD6405-CSTATUS
                        , :COCD6405-CUSERID
                        ,  CURRENT TIMESTAMP
                        , :COCD6405-GREFINV
                        , :COCD6405-DPAG
                        , :COCD6405-CTIPDOC
                        , :COCD6405-CMOEDA
                        , :COCD6405-CIMPOSTO
                        , :COCD6405-NOTAS
                        , :COCD6405-NTOTCTRV
                        , :COCD6405-NTAXCTRV
                        , :COCD6405-CTIPFAC
                        , :COCD6405-NTOTPAG
                        , :COCD6405-NTAXPAG
                        , :COCD6405-NTOTRET
                        , :COCD6405-NTAXRET
                        , :COCD6405-CTIPMOV
                        , :COCD6405-IRECON
                        , :COCD6405-DDATMOV
                        , :COCD6405-NSEQMOV
                        , :COCD6405-GREFNCR
                        , :COCD6405-DDATEMINCR
                        , :COCD6405-CPAIS
                        , :COCD6405-CBANCO
                        , :COCD6405-CCONTA
                   )
              END-EXEC

              MOVE CON-COVT6405 TO VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME

              PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
                 THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT

              EVALUATE TRUE
              WHEN DB2-OK
                   CONTINUE
              WHEN OTHER
                   SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                   MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                   MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                   MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                   MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                   PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                      THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
              END-EVALUATE
           END-IF.

       2600-INS-INVPAY-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2610-OBTEM-SEQ.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2610-OBTEM-SEQ'       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
              SELECT COUNT(NSEQ)
                INTO :WS-NSEQ
                FROM COVT6405_INVPAY
               WHERE NIDINVOICE  = :COCD6405-NIDINVOICE
                 AND NIDPROJECTO = :COCD6405-NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT6405               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN DB2-OK
                    ADD 1                       TO WS-NSEQ
                    MOVE WS-NSEQ                TO COCD6405-NSEQ
               WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                    CONTINUE
               WHEN OTHER
                    SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                    MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                    MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                    MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                    MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                    PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                       THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2610-OBTEM-SEQ-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2700-UPD-INVOICES.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2700-UPD-INVOICES'        TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCK0002-CSTATUS-PAG     TO COCD5013-CSTATUS
           MOVE WS-PROGNAME              TO COCD5013-CUSERID
           MOVE COCD6900-DDATMOV         TO COCD5013-DPAG
           MOVE CON-S                    TO COCD5013-IRECON
           MOVE COCD6900-DDATMOV         TO COCD5013-DDATMOV
           MOVE COCD6900-NSEQMOV         TO COCD5013-NSEQMOV

           COMPUTE COCD5013-NTOTPAG = COCD5013-NTOTALAMOUNT -
                                      COCD5013-NTOTRET

           COMPUTE COCD5013-NTAXPAG = COCD5013-NTAXAMOUNT -
                                      COCD5013-NTAXRET

           EXEC SQL
                 UPDATE COVT5013_INVOICES
                 SET    CSTATUS      = :COCD5013-CSTATUS
                      , CUSERID      = :COCD5013-CUSERID
                      , HTIMEST      =  CURRENT TIMESTAMP
                      , DPAG         = :COCD5013-DPAG
                      , NTOTPAG      = :COCD5013-NTOTPAG
                      , NTAXPAG      = :COCD5013-NTAXPAG
                      , IRECON       = :COCD5013-IRECON
                      , DDATMOV      = :COCD5013-DDATMOV
                      , NSEQMOV      = :COCD5013-NSEQMOV
                  WHERE NIDPROJECTO  = :COCD5013-NIDPROJECTO
                    AND NIDINVOICE   = :COCD5013-NIDINVOICE
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT5013               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2700-UPD-INVOICES-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       2800-UPD-MOV-BANC.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '2800-UPD-MOV-BANC'        TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE WS-PROGNAME              TO COCD6900-CUSERID
           MOVE CON-S                    TO COCD6900-IRECON
           MOVE COCD5013-GREFINV         TO COCD6900-GREFINV

           EXEC SQL
                 UPDATE COVT6900_MOVBANC
                 SET    IRECON       = :COCD6900-IRECON
                      , GREFINV      = :COCD6900-GREFINV
                      , NINVREC      =  NINVREC + 1
                      , CUSERID      = :COCD6900-CUSERID
                      , HTIMEST      =  CURRENT TIMESTAMP
                  WHERE CPAIS        = :COCD6900-CPAIS
                    AND CBANCO       = :COCD6900-CBANCO
                    AND CCONTA       = :COCD6900-CCONTA
                    AND DDATMOV      = :COCD6900-DDATMOV
                    AND NSEQMOV      = :COCD6900-NSEQMOV
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT6900               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
           WHEN DB2-OK
                CONTINUE
           WHEN OTHER
                SET  AQCW0009-RCODE-APL     TO TRUE
                MOVE WS-PROGNAME            TO AQCW0100-PGMNAME
                MOVE VIAL0015-CALLER-ID     TO AQCW0100-PARAGRAPH
                MOVE VIAW0012-TABLE-NAME    TO AQCW0100-NM-ENTIDADE
                MOVE VIAW0012-SQLCODE       TO AQCW0100-SQLCODE
                PERFORM AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG
                   THRU AQCP0100-ESCREVE-MSG-EXIT
           END-EVALUATE.

       2800-UPD-MOV-BANC-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
       3000-FIM-PROGRAMA.
      ******************************************************************
           MOVE '3000-FIM-PROGRAMA'         TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID.

           IF AQCW0100-AT-DEBUG-SIM
              PERFORM VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0015-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      * Processos finais
            PERFORM AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE
               THRU AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE-EXIT.

            PERFORM AQCP0002-TRATA-SYNCPOINT
               THRU AQCP0002-TRATA-SYNCPOINT-EXIT.

           PERFORM AQCP0100-REG-FIM
              THRU AQCP0100-REG-FIM-EXIT.

       3000-FIM-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      ******************************************************************
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE AQCP0002 END-EXEC.
      ******************************************************************
           COPY AQCP0009.
           COPY AQCP0109.
           COPY VIAP0011.
           COPY VIAP0012.
           COPY VIAP0015.
           COPY VIAP1000.
      ******************************************************************
